high_descs: head to the desk in the corner
Take the pencil from the desk
Turn around twice, put the pencil on the desk
anns.task_desc: Take the pencil from the desk, put it back on the desk

high_descs: Turn right at the trash can and walk to the left of the bed. Turn left at the desk to your left.
Pick up the white pencil on the desk.
Put the pencil back down on the desk by the books.
anns.task_desc: Walk to the desk and pick up a pencil also put it back.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk past the desk, then turn left and go to the end of the desk, closest to the wall.
Pick up the pencil on the desk, to the right of the lamp.
Move over to your left slightly so that you are right next to the blue office chair.
Place the pencil back on the desk, in front of the keys.
anns.task_desc: Move the pencil on the desk over.
